     <span class="dvl">
     </span>
     4.14
    </span>
    = 1.48
   </span>
  </p>
  <p>Design spans lengths and edge moments in adjacent panels</p>
  <img alt="ssfs-span.png" class="side" src="Images/structures/rc/spans/ssfs-span.png" style="height:140pt;"/>
