  <h4>Loads</h4>
  <p>Characteristic uniform loads</p>
  <p>
   Self weight -
   <span class="eq">
    <var>g</var>
    <sub>sw</sub>
    = 0.25 ·
    <var>h</var>
    = 0.25 · 14 = 3.5
   </span>
   kN/m²
  </p>
  <p>
   Permanent -
   <span class="eq">
    <var>g</var>
    <sub>k</sub>
    =
    <u class="input-33">2.5</u>
   </span>
   kN/m²
  </p>
  <p>
   Variable -
   <span class="eq">
    <var>q</var>
    <sub>k</sub>
    =
    <u class="input-34">2</u>
   </span>
   kN/m²
  </p>
  <p>
   Partial safety factor -
   <span class="eq">
    <var>γ</var>
    <sub>G</sub>
    = 1.35
   </span>
   ;
   <span class="eq">
    <var>γ</var>
    <sub>Q</sub>
    = 1.5
   </span>
  </p>
  <p>Design uniform loads</p>
  <p>
   <span class="eq">
    <var>p</var>
    =  (
    <var>g</var>
    <sub>sw</sub>
    +
    <var>g</var>
    <sub>k</sub>
    )  ·
    <var>γ</var>
    <sub>G</sub>
    +
    <var>q</var>
    <sub>k</sub>
    ·
    <var>γ</var>
    <sub>Q</sub>
    =  ( 3.5 + 2.5 )  · 1.35 + 2 · 1.5 = 11.1
   </span>
   kN/m²
  </p>
